item.title: ~~@$$^help~~@$$^
item.dc:creator: @Owner_Tony-Scape Owner Tony-Scape
item.description:
@Owner_Tony-Scape wrote:

Go to “Client.java” then search what it says like “Welcome to spades-Scape” Search that. Ctrl F, then put that in. Then you can edit it. Click the X on the top and it will say “Are you sure you want to save?” “Yes or No” Click yes, then compile your server and turn ur server on, and there you go!!

Hope it works! =]
